ler feature, which co-stars \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/travis-scott\"\u003eTravis Scott\u003c/a\u003e. The entire film is shot with thermal cameras, giving it the feeling of a video game cut scene. Adding to that vibe is the voiceover from Jordi Mollà, the actor who leads the film as a hitman in a devastated world. “The old world is no more,” he growls at the beginning. “No more truths. I was born to kill.” Watch the trailer above, and read our review of the film \u003ca href=\"https://www.thefader.com/2023/10/26/rap-column-aggro-dr1ft-travis-scott-review\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e.\n\nAside from \u003ci\u003eAGGRO DR1FT\u003c/i\u003e‘s premiere, Travis Scott spent the year preparing for \u003ca href=\"https://www.thefader.com/2023/07/28/new-music-friday-stream-projects-from-travis-scott-aphex-twin-madeline-kenney-and-more\"\u003ethe July release of his album \u003ci\u003eUtopia\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. The album featured \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/drake\"\u003eDrake\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/the-weeknd\"\u003eThe Weeknd\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/kanye-west\"\u003eKanye West\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/21-savage\"\u003e21 Savage\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"http://www.thefader.com/artist/rob49\"\u003eRob49\u003c/a\u003e, and others. He’s currently touring behind the project. Last September, he sat down for a deposition in \u003ca href=\"https://www.thefader.com/2023/09/19/travis-scott-sits-for-astroworld-civil-deposition\"\u003ethe ongoing civil lawsuit against alleging his culpability in the 2021 Astroworld tragedy\u003c/a\u003e, where 10 people were killed and thousands injured in a crowd surge during Scott’s headlining set at his annual festival. Houston Police \u003ca href=\"https://www.thefader.com/2023/07/28/read-houston-polices-report-on-the-astroworld-2021-tragedy\"\u003ecleared him of possible criminal charges\u003