                <h1>Congress launches Astroworld investigation</h1>
                <h2 class="deck">The House Oversight and Reform Committee has opened an investigation into the events surrounding the Astroworld 2021 tragedy.</h2>

            </div>

          </div>

          
          <div class="credits gutter_left triple_gutter_right">
              <div class="author">
    <span>
      By <span class="credit_name"><a href="/contributor/raphael-helfand">Raphael Helfand</a></span>
  </div>


<div class="posted">
  <div>
    December 22, 2021
  </div>
</div>

          </div>

